Add sleuth dependency
Add Sample bean in main class
https://www.erlang.org/patches/otp-25.3.2
https://www.rabbitmq.com/install-windows.html
Add Zipkin and amqp dependencies in all microservices.
Running Rabbit Mq:-
	Open Cmd
	Go to sbin folder path
	rabbitmq-plugins enable rabbitmq_management
	Go to services in Windows and restart rabbit server
	localhost:15672 ..... username/password by default guest.

Downlowd Zipkin jar from Zipkin quickstart and select java version
Running Zipkin server:-
	open cmd
	go to zipkin jar folder
	Connect zipkin with Rabbitmq :- set RABBIT_URI=amqp://localhost
	java -jar zipkin-server-2.24.3-exec.jar
	hit :- localhost:9411/zipkin
